graphql.query:
# Write your query or mutation here
query GetMasterRoutes($businessUnitId: Int!, $limit: Int, $skip: Int) {
  masterRoutes(businessUnitId: $businessUnitId, limit: $limit, skip: $skip) {
    id
    published
    serviceDaysList
    assignedServiceDaysList
    businessUnitId
    name
    color
    status
    publishDate
    truckId
    driverId
    serviceItems {
      id
      haulingId
      serviceFrequencyId
      jobSiteId
      jobSite {
        id
        address {
          addressLine1
          addressLine2
          fullAddress
          city
          state
          zip
        }
        location
        coordinates
      }
      billableServiceId
      billableServiceDescription
      businessLineId
      materialId
      subscriptionId
      businessUnitId
      startDate
      equipmentItemId
      serviceDaysOfWeek
      serviceAreaId
      endDate
      bestTimeToComeFrom
      bestTimeToComeTo
      sequence
    }
    createdAt
